'''奶油刮刀'''（Butter curler），或稱'''奶油捲製器'''，是一種用來製作食用裝飾[[鮮奶油|奶油]]的廚具。也可用來刮[[巧克力|巧克力]]與[[蠟|蠟]]。通常被刮物會先冷卻而刮刀會先泡在溫水裡讓切削更加容易。<ref>{{cite book | last=Berolzheimer | first=Ruth | year=1988 | title=Culinary Arts Institute Encyclopedic Cookbook | edition=1st | url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=eoktyOUwM1oC&lpg=PA45&dq=%22butter%20curler%22&pg=PA45#v=onepage&q=%22butter%20curler%22&f=false | accessdate=2010-12-24 | archive-date=2012-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108095602/http://books.google.ca/books?id=eoktyOUwM1oC&lpg=PA45&dq=%22butter%20curler%22&pg=PA45#v=onepage&q=%22butter%20curler%22&f=false | dead-url=no }} page 45.</ref>

